## What's Changed
* feat: add SQLite analyzer and some assorted changes by @quetz in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/484
* feat: add `--archive-browsing` flag to show zip/jar files as dirs, add `--collapse-path` flag to for collapsing single-child directory 
* feat: add `--depth` flag by @sguptasf in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/485
* feat: add options to force output units by @shuaixr in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/464
* feat: allow excluding file(s) by their type  by @AmauMaill in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/472
* feat: bump version of go and badger by @joy4eg in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/438
* feat: time filters by @Sarke in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/425
* feat: bump versions of dependencies by @dundee in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/450
chains  by @bingoohuang in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/434
* fix: non-deterministic ordering in ParallelAnalyzer by @ShivamB25 in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/445
* docs: add mise alternative method installation by @jylenhof in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/465
* chore: bump Go to 1.25.5 to fix crypto/x509 CVEs by @almeida-silas in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/471

## New Contributors
* @joy4eg made their first contribution in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/438

* @jylenhof made their first contribution in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/465
* @almeida-silas made their first contribution in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/471
* @AmauMaill made their first contribution in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/472
* @sguptasf made their first contribution in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/485
* @quetz made their first contribution in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/484

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/dundee/gdu/compare/v5.32.0...v5.33.0
